HEADWORD: Fourteen
<hw>Four"teen`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>fourtene</ets>, <ets>feowertene</ets>, AS.
<ets>fe⟦oacute⟧wert⟦ymac⟧ne</ets>, <ets>fe⟦oacute⟧wert⟦emac⟧ne</ets>.
