==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Fourteen
<hw>Four"teen`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The sum of ten and
four; forteen units or objects.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A symbol representing fourteen, as 14 or
xiv.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fourteenth</ent>⟦br⟧
